f=Governance/precedent/custom/ruling-log/assets/ruling-schema.md · h1:Ruling Record Schema precedent/ruling-log=`ruling_id: <R-YYYY-NNN>              # sequential per year \· date: <YYYY-MM-DD> \· case: <the decision under review, one line> \· scope: <venture/unit, or "company"> \· gates_run: [constitution-enforcement, strategic-veto, fiduciary-guard,` · h1:Ruling Record Schema precedent/ruling-log=One record board ruling, appended configured decision log. Append-only: corrections new records referencing original `ruling_id`. · h2:Field notes=**rationale** mandatory ruling. "Rationale captured" valid (and flagged) value; reconstructed rationale not., **operator_final_call** records disagreement between board operator instructive records log., **outcome** turns log decision list learning set: rulings whose outcomes contradicted rationale exactly what consistency-check quarterly reviews surface.